description:
A worn and used bible, barely legible. A bible such as
this must have been read over and over.
name: Tattered Bible

description:
A simple walking stick. However, it is said that
such humble staves brought about great miracles.
name: Walking Stick

description:
In order to combat the rising threat of Beasts, even
commoners would carry such crosses around.
name: Wooden Cross

description:
Weapon of the Angel infantry, a holy bow that pierces
sinners.
name: Angel's Bow

description:
Said to have been used by a Judge to slay 1000 men.
Some residual power can still be felt...
name: Donkey's Jawbone

description:
A stronger bow given to the Angel elite. Only an angel
who has proven themselves can hope to weild it.
name: Archangel's Bow

description:
A hip and fresh Bible updated for the youth of today!
Radical!
name: Extreme Teen Bible!

description:
A staff with a curved hook for managing sheep. However
it is also known to be handy for fending off Beasts.
name: Shepherd's Crook

description:
A finely made cross variant, carried only by the Kryma
Priesthood.
name: Metal Cross

description:
A thick, heavy bible carried by those in the 
Priesthood. In pristine condition, perhaps never read.
name: Hardcover Bible

description:
A rod used by the Priesthood, symbolizing 
their status before God.
name: Priest's Staff

description:
The highest of Angel weapons, given only to those 
chosen by God. Pierces sin with unyielding light.
name: Seraphim's Crossbow

description:
A bejeweled cross made of solid gold. All who see it
know that the owner is truly faithful.
name: Golden Cross

description:
Creation of Mastema, Demon of Knowledge. A bible filled
with sinful words. Once equipped, it cannot be removed.
name: Black Bible

description:
Creation of Mastema. A cross that defies God. 
Once equipped, it cannot be removed.
name: Inverted Cross

description:
Creation of Mastema. Even an angel's weapon can be  
corrupted. Once equipped, it cannot be removed.
name: Fallen Angel Bow
